The evidence with the title 'The political performances of Peng Liyuan | Wilson Center ' says Jan 27, 2017  ... In 2013 , when her husband, Communist Party (CCP) general secretary Xi Jinping , began his first term, Peng became a leading cultural component of Xi's soft power  ... Clad in a red silk ball gown , she sashayed across the stage as state television producers rolled video of schoolchildren waving red flags . 
